This photo is a series of photos that has become a cult photo in the World. He won the photo of the year award at the Siena International photography competition. The photo belongs to a Syrian family. Baba Munzir lost his right leg as a result of a bomb falling while walking around the market in Idlib, Syria. At that time, Mustafa, who was born from the chemical gas he breathed while his mother was pregnant, was born without limbs. After the award he received in the competition, the photo came to the agenda of many newspapers and television. One of those who shared these posts is Angelina Jolie.

